#Account Activity

**Account Activity** allows you to see a complete overview of any of your Dentists.

To access **Account Activity** follow these steps:

* Open **Account Activity** from teh contents bar

* Select the account you wish to view from the dropdown menu and click **Refresh**

* This will then show you all **Invoices** *(paid and unpaid)*, **Payments** *(allocated and unallocated*), Credit Notes and Balances.

* You will also see a breakdown of the **Age Debt** on the account.

You can also **Post a Balance** in **Account Activity**;

* In the **Post a Balance** section enter a **Description, Amount and Date** then click **Post**. 
